graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Component"
        Frontend[Frontend<br/>React/TypeScript SPA<br/>PatternFly UI]
        Backend[Backend<br/>Node.js/Fastify<br/>Port 8080/TCP]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift OAuth<br/>Port 8443/TCP HTTPS]

        OAuthProxy -->|reverse proxy| Backend
        Backend -->|serves static assets| Frontend
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resource Definitions"
        AcceleratorProfile[AcceleratorProfile<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhApplication[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhDashboardConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhDocument[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhQuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>9091/TCP HTTP]
        Route[OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        DSC[DataScienceCluster CR]
        DSCI[DSCInitialization CR]
        Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks CR]
        ServingRuntimes[KServe ServingRuntimes CR]
        ModelRegistry[ModelRegistry CR]
        ModelRegistrySvc[Model Registry Service<br/>HTTP API]
        DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>HTTP API]
        TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service<br/>HTTP API]
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS 443/TCP| Route
    Route -->|HTTPS 8443/TCP<br/>TLS Reencrypt| OAuthProxy

    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OAuthServer
    Backend -->|watches/manages| AcceleratorProfile
    Backend -->|reads| OdhApplication
    Backend -->|CRUD operations| OdhDashboardConfig
    Backend -->|reads| OdhDocument
    Backend -->|reads| OdhQuickStart

    Backend -->|HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Service Account Token| K8sAPI
    Backend -->|reads| DSC
    Backend -->|reads| DSCI
    Backend -->|CRUD operations| Notebooks
    Backend -->|CRUD operations| ServingRuntimes
    Backend -->|CRUD operations| ModelRegistry
    Backend -->|HTTP API queries| ModelRegistrySvc
    Backend -->|HTTP API queries| DSPipelines
    Backend -->|HTTP API queries| TrustyAI
    Backend -->|HTTP 9091/TCP<br/>Bearer Token| Prometheus

